design-lint
===========

This tool embeds and modifies the anti-pattern detection engine from the
"impeccable" project:

    impeccable — https://github.com/pbakaus/impeccable
    Copyright (c) 2026 Paul Bakaus
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see LICENSE).

Modifications made in this distribution:
  - Vendored only cli/engine/** (the detection engine); the npm CLI installer,
    skills bundle, and web build are not included.
  - Ported the URL/visual scanning path from Puppeteer to Astral
    (jsr:@astral/astral) via an import-map shim (shims/puppeteer-astral.mjs)
    so the tool runs under Deno with no npm/node_modules. Engine source files
    under src/engine/** are unmodified from upstream.

The Apache-2.0 license requires retention of the above copyright notice and
this statement of changes.
